body:
That's because tf.nn.rnn doesn't exist anymore! Perhaps you are looking for [tf.nn.dynamic_rnn](https://www.tensorflow.org/api_docs/python/tf/nn/dynamic_rnn) or the more experimental [tf.nn.raw_rnn](https://www.tensorflow.org/api_docs/python/tf/nn/raw_rnn)?

Alternativley there is the contrib repo of RNN function in [tf.contrib.rnn](https://www.tensorflow.org/api_docs/python/tf/contrib/rnn)
